data.description: Lovely Home in the Westfield Addition of Otter Creek! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has been updated with new carpet, all new light fixtures and has been freshly painted throughout. The kitchen is furnished with new SS gas range, microwave, dishwasher, and new SS refrigerator. Tray ceilings in the living room and master! Master bedroom is equipped with a walk-in shower, jetted tup and large walk-in closet. Large fenced backyard and two car garage. Come see!
